<h1 class="team-member--name">Mark Pollack</h1>
<div class="team-member--sub-info">
<p>Spring Cloud Data Flow lead</p>
<p>New York, NY</p>
</div>
<div class="team-member--bio">Mark Pollack is a software engineer with Pivotal and is the lead of the Spring Cloud Data Flow project. He has been a contributor to many Spring projects dating back to the Spring Framework in 2003 as well as founding the Spring.NET and Spring Data projects.</div>
</div>
